wb-mcu-fw-updater (1.3.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * added stopbits-tolerant instrument (only in bootloader now)
  * added -T / --serial-timeout arg to some modes:
    * update-fw/update-bl: all communications (except in-bootloader flashing)
    * recover: only for asking fw_signature
    * flash-file: only for jumping to bootloader

 -- Vladimir Romanov <v.romanov@wirenboard.ru>  Thu, 5 May 2022 20:28:37 +0300

